# Copy to .recaptcha.env (same directory) and set the site key from:
#   Firebase Console → Build → App Check → Apps → Web (perezfans) →
#   reCAPTCHA **Enterprise** (or matching provider) — same site key as GCP / web/index.html meta.
# Keys from `gcloud recaptcha keys list` only work if that same key is registered
# in App Check for this web app; otherwise you get HTTP 400 on token exchange.
#
# Public site key (same as web/index.html meta when using current “perezfans” key).
RECAPTCHA_SITE_KEY=6LeBRqIsAAAAAOWXICKGW5Lt0NTIDMlGHXWN2vS0
